snippet.title: X-Men: Legends (PS2/Xbox/GC) (2004) Video Game US Ad/Commercial
snippet.description:
US Ad/Commercial for the X-Men: Legends video game.

Platforms in which this game was released: PlayStation 2, Xbox, Nintendo GameCube
Also released on N-Gage, not covered in this Ad/Commercial.
